<ul>
<li>To secure your Bitcoin wallet, use a&nbsp;reputable provider with strong security, a&nbsp;hardware wallet for your private keys and create strong passwords</li>



<li>Recovery options include using backup files or seeking professional assistance from companies that specialize in recovering lost cryptocurrency wallets like Wallet Recovery Services</li>



